title: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Legislative Districts - Senate, Oregon, 2000
name: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, Legislative Districts - Senate, Oregon, 2000
description:
The Oregon Senate Districts theme was created by merging blocks from the census 2000 redistricting blocks theme using the Autobound Redistricting extension. The polygons formed by the merged blocks represent the boundaries of the Oregon House districts. Two house districts were than merged to create each Senate District. 
Purpose: To delineate Oregon House Districts.

author.source: Oregon Secretary of State's office; Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office
